text: Emil Schwegler (April 22, 1879 - May 19, 1968) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1968 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:People from Basel-Stadt
